      "date": "2014-11-07 20:28:54.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review+1\n\nThis makes me wonder why it wasn't possible to reproduce this behaviour in a test system with the OST deactivated?  Is the problem only present if the OST has never connected to the MDS before?\n\nIt would be useful to get a test case for this, where the MDS is stopped along with OST0001 and then the MDS is restarted without the OST to see if this can reproduce the problem and if this patch fixes it.",
